      "text": "Today, I had the sincere joy of honoring two Fourth District FFA students who were elected as Indiana FFA officers on the House Floor.\n\nI'm also glad to have met with the entire @IndianaFFA officer team while they were in Washington!\n\nCongratulations, Jessie, Katie, and all the https://t.co/tzd8CjtXYd",
