      "text": "I applaud @USFWS for rescinding this inane and wasteful regulatory rule that has harmed the producers who help feed and fuel America. Overuse of the Endangered Species Act has given unelected bureaucrats too much control over people’s lives.\nhttps://t.co/m6PtaLL4Ov",
